1
00:01:32,190 --> 00:01:34,990
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:38,030
[Episode 30]

3
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:40,479
You.

4
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,640
Take him away.

5
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:45,500
And you.

6
00:01:47,870 --> 00:01:48,200
Move!

7
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,580
Get out.

8
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,420
How is it going?

9
00:01:53,789 --> 00:01:54,990
-It's freezing out here.
-This one.

10
00:01:54,990 --> 00:01:55,870
-Come out.
-Take him away.

11
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:57,509
And you had to come out here
and go through this with us.

12
00:01:57,509 --> 00:01:58,840
Are the higher-ups not planning

13
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,270
to promote you anymore?

14
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,950
Are you blind?

15
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:04,010
Alright, alright.

16
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,110
Sorry.

17
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:06,740
And you!

18
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:10,400
You,

19
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,370
come out.

20
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:16,990
Take him away!

21
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,079
Take him away!

22
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:24,750
You!

23
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,090
Take him away

24
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,710
for inspection.

25
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:30,040
Move.

26
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:31,240
Move!

27
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:32,510
Take him away!

28
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,800
Turn around.

29
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,310
What are you doing here?

30
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,370
Search carefully!

31
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:39,150
You,

32
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:39,870
go over there!

33
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:40,730
What's inside?

34
00:02:44,430 --> 00:02:45,030
"Surprise."

35
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:45,310
You.

36
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:46,710
-What?
-Come out!

37
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,690
"Surprise."

38
00:02:48,150 --> 00:02:49,079
Speak clearly.

39
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,840
Supplies.

40
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:50,500
Food!

41
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:52,370
Alright.

42
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:53,560
Go do something else.

43
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,760
I'll watch this cart.

44
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,470
You,

45
00:02:55,710 --> 00:02:56,640
-come here.
-Go.

46
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,680
What are you doing?

47
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:05,410
-Move the supplies out quickly.
-Take him away!

48
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,330
So much trouble every day.

49
00:03:15,910 --> 00:03:16,310
Get in!

50
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:36,820
Relax. It's me.

51
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:38,040
Why did you push me?

52
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,800
What rank am I and what rank are you?

53
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,200
Power-abusing wretch.

54
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,010
I've been roughing it outside,

55
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,630
and when I get back I still have to
take crap from you Imperial Guards!

56
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:46,360
Exactly.

57
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,760
If you don't give us an explanation today,

58
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:51,620
the Central Army will make you pay for it!

59
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,190
Yeah!

60
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:52,800
Yeah!

61
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,590
Arresting people for no reason—

62
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:55,710
what right do you have to do this?

63
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:56,440
Stand still!

64
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,500
Once Lord Cao finishes the verification...

65
00:03:58,500 --> 00:03:59,000
Listen.

66
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,800
You'll be released!

67
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,930
Since you know how to steal,

68
00:04:00,930 --> 00:04:03,360
you should know
how to do the opposite, right?

69
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:04,530
What are you doing?

70
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:23,920
What's taking you so long?

71
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,330
It's too heavy. I can't move it.

72
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,080
You brat!

73
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,310
Don't think I'll go easy on you

74
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:32,720
just because you're from my hometown.

75
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,260
What are you doing?

76
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:42,960
Do you know what this is?

77
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:44,560
I do.

78
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:46,730
Do you know its power?

79
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,030
I do.

80
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:50,710
If you dare call for help,

81
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,360
your emperor...

82
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,740
will send you to your death immediately.

83
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,409
I promise it will be grand.

84
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:57,600
Emperor?

85
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:09,220
Your Majesty, haven't you...

86
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,100
I have a bad temper

87
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:13,820
and love killing loud people.

88
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,630
You know that.

89
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,190
I do. I do.

90
00:05:20,310 --> 00:05:22,170
You also shouldn't be this quiet.

91
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,480
Yes, yes.

92
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,390
I mean,

93
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,720
if you ever need me for anything,

94
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,200
I will do everything I can,

95
00:05:29,310 --> 00:05:30,770
even at the cost of my life.

96
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:39,520
My legs are numb from standing.

97
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:42,730
Yeah.

98
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,470
Move!

99
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,360
Are you done yet?

100
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:54,870
Be polite.

101
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:55,460
Hurry up.

102
00:05:56,190 --> 00:05:57,000
Watch your hands.

103
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,360
It's all orders from above.

104
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,360
Cut us some slack.

105
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:03,900
Are we done?

106
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,450
Exactly.

107
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,440
Seize him!

108
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,820
This isn't mine!

109
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,380
You're framing me!

110
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,390
Let me go!

111
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:23,160
Let me go!

112
00:06:24,850 --> 00:06:25,470
Lord Cao,

113
00:06:25,870 --> 00:06:27,070
this was found on him.

114
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,290
Report it to Prince Duan.

115
00:06:31,290 --> 00:06:31,630
Yes!

116
00:06:32,130 --> 00:06:33,270
This isn't mine!

117
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:34,450
You're framing me!

118
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,520
Tear off his face.

119
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,860
What are you doing?

120
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:41,940
My Lord,

121
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:43,920
This person isn't wearing a disguise.

122
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,720
Take him away.

123
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,460
Wait, Lord Cao!

124
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:51,240
Lord Cao,

125
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,800
what is the meaning of this?

126
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,659
We are investigating spies within the army

127
00:06:55,659 --> 00:06:57,260
under Prince Duan's orders.

128
00:06:57,430 --> 00:06:59,460
We ask for your full cooperation

129
00:06:59,490 --> 00:07:01,820
so that no important matters are delayed.

130
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:02,690
Lord Cao,

131
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,690
the person you've arrested

132
00:07:06,310 --> 00:07:07,880
is my cousin,

133
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:10,300
Li Wang, a centurion

134
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:11,760
of the Central Army.

135
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:13,490
If you say

136
00:07:13,750 --> 00:07:14,600
he is a spy,

137
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,120
does that make me one too?

138
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,620
Or the whole Central Army?

139
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,630
Or even

140
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,080
the Three Armies?

141
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:25,010
Deputy General Li,

142
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,360
I never meant that.

143
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,870
It's just that the item found on him

144
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:31,890
is something used by that demonic consort,
Yu Wanyin.

145
00:07:31,890 --> 00:07:33,720
I'm only bringing him back to ask

146
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:36,510
a few questions
to avoid any misunderstandings.

147
00:07:36,510 --> 00:07:37,370
Ask questions?

148
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,260
Li Wang!

149
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:39,770
Here!

150
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:40,990
Is this yours?

151
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,560
No!

152
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:43,430
I asked.

153
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,690
He said it's not his.

154
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,500
Well...

155
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,290
Release him.

156
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:47,950
Release him!

157
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:48,350
You...

158
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,370
You...

159
00:07:49,590 --> 00:07:50,920
Are you trying to rebel?

160
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,280
It's the Central Army!

161
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,100
I saw it!

162
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:07,310
It came from the Central Army's side!

163
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:09,520
Let's go!

164
00:08:10,020 --> 00:08:10,360
Go!

165
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:12,750
Your Majesty,
you're getting better with guns.

166
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:13,550
You're wrong.

167
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,730
It's a crossbow.

168
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,630
Nine Heavens Mystical Fire
Sleeve Crossbow.

169
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:18,560
Mr. Bei named it.

170
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,410
Don't call it by the wrong name.

171
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:25,270
Let's go!

172
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,060
Flower!

173
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:01,480
You go first.

174
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,230
Where is His Majesty?

175
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:09,760
Your Majesty!

176
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,870
Xiahou Dan!

177
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,080
I'm here!

178
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:10,480
Everyone entering the palace
must be searched again.

179
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:12,260
Generals,

180
00:10:12,790 --> 00:10:13,920
please understand.

181
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:15,610
There was never any search

182
00:10:15,890 --> 00:10:17,820
when we entered the palace before.

183
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,910
Now you keep
making things difficult for us.

184
00:10:19,910 --> 00:10:21,710
What exactly is your intention?

185
00:10:22,640 --> 00:10:24,670
I'm only following orders.

186
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,540
Please, generals,

187
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:27,500
forgive me.

188
00:10:28,530 --> 00:10:29,130
Eunuch An,

189
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:31,360
it's not that we are being difficult.

190
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,510
After a forced march
of thousands of miles,

191
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,240
the troops are already on edge.

192
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:37,190
Could you ask Prince Duan to come

193
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,890
and clarify this in person?

194
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:42,910
If I remember correctly,

195
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,040
Eunuch An,

196
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,550
you serve at His Majesty's side.

197
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,320
Why is it that now,

198
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,200
when Prince Duan is in power,

199
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:53,750
he still uses the Emperor's old servant
to send messages?

200
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:56,070
Deputy General Lin, I...

201
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,020
don't quite...

202
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:59,480
understand what you're implying.

203
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:00,700
Could it be that

204
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:04,120
His Highness is being controlled by you?

205
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,960
Report!

206
00:11:06,630 --> 00:11:08,110
The Central Army is staging a rebellion!

207
00:11:08,110 --> 00:11:08,670
What?

208
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:12,220
The Central Army is staging a rebellion!

209
00:11:16,070 --> 00:11:16,570
What?

210
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,210
What's going on?

211
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:20,350
What exactly is happening?

212
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,490
Report!

213
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,180
Commander Lei!

214
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,630
The Imperial Guards
asked us to provide support!

215
00:11:24,630 --> 00:11:25,390
Shall we go?

216
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:26,720
Report!

217
00:11:26,930 --> 00:11:27,840
The Central Army sent a message,

218
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,690
also asking us for help!

219
00:11:28,690 --> 00:11:29,350
Shall we go?

220
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:30,490
This...

221
00:11:30,490 --> 00:11:31,090
Come on...

222
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,200
How would I know?

223
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,210
Aren't we on the same side?

224
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,860
Commander, what should we do?

225
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,320
Well...

226
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:42,960
Come here!

227
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,470
Hurry up and go to the Right Army!

228
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:45,530
See what they say!

229
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:45,870
Yes!

230
00:11:45,870 --> 00:11:46,870
Hurry! Go, go, go!

231
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,290
His Majesty said

232
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:51,630
our goal is to put

233
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:53,360
the situation under control
as quickly as possible

234
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,630
and minimize casualties.

235
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,830
Do you all understand

236
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:56,750
what to do?

237
00:11:56,910 --> 00:11:57,710
Yes!

238
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,120
Defensive unit, step forward!

239
00:11:59,120 --> 00:11:59,670
Yes!

240
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:00,730
The rest of you,

241
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:01,910
grab your weapons

242
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:03,070
and follow me!

243
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,600
Yes!

244
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,720
Report!

245
00:12:09,750 --> 00:12:10,480
What did the Right Army say?

246
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,200
They said that

247
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,550
since they abandoned us
after getting what they wanted,

248
00:12:13,550 --> 00:12:14,080
we fight!

249
00:12:15,410 --> 00:12:16,300
♪ Who stakes a claim? ♪

250
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:16,050
Well...

251
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:16,790
He's right, Commander.

252
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:18,160
♪ In the end,
whose hands will destiny fall into? ♪

253
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,660
Deputy General Zhou
went into the city alone.

254
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:19,290
♪ Treading through fire ♪

255
00:12:19,370 --> 00:12:21,120
♪ Who dares to probe these truths? ♪

256
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:22,370
They're taking advantage
of our lack of leadership!

257
00:12:21,330 --> 00:12:22,790
♪ Relying only on my courage ♪

258
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:24,220
♪ I roam this world ♪

259
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:23,930
Commander,

260
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,000
do we fight or not?

261
00:12:24,450 --> 00:12:25,650
♪ Bright light exposes the evil ♪

262
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:25,790
Which side should we attack?

263
00:12:25,710 --> 00:12:26,340
♪ Let me break through ♪

264
00:12:26,410 --> 00:12:27,550
♪ The gap on this path to the underworld ♪

265
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,600
The Imperial Guards, of course.

266
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,760
♪ Thousands of lights
illuminate layers of mist ♪

267
00:12:28,870 --> 00:12:30,580
♪ Forged in blazing fire,
I steel my bones for battle ♪

268
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,470
Let's fight!

269
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:32,320
Kill!

270
00:12:30,770 --> 00:12:32,060
♪ Turning the world around,
the empire resounds ♪

271
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:33,420
♪ In the chaos,
shadows linger in every corner ♪

272
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,930
♪ Truth or lies, the more you hide,
the more it shows ♪

273
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:36,340
♪ Messages come from all directions,
like a game of hide and seek ♪

274
00:12:36,530 --> 00:12:37,860
♪ Players in the game
wear masks as they clash ♪

275
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:39,410
♪ Ghostly flames and loyal hearts,
who will load the first shot? ♪

276
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:44,320
Kill!

277
00:12:39,610 --> 00:12:40,750
♪ Stamping approval in cinnabar ♪

278
00:12:40,830 --> 00:12:42,500
♪ Yet the ink
doesn't always mark the truth ♪

279
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,660
♪ In the rolls of fame ♪

280
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:45,480
♪ Not all deeds are genuine ♪

281
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:46,590
♪ Even with
a petition signed by 10,000 people ♪

282
00:12:46,610 --> 00:12:48,260
♪ You may never make it
onto the merit list ♪

283
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:52,720
Kill!

284
00:12:48,350 --> 00:12:49,450
♪ In the box of merit ♪

285
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:50,860
♪ It might not be the Bodhisattva's face ♪

286
00:12:50,930 --> 00:12:53,140
♪ What a world,
each step full of schemes ♪

287
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:55,980
♪ Danger hides everywhere,
and life's like gambling ♪

288
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:59,030
Kill!

289
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:56,620
[Capital of Xia]

290
00:12:56,220 --> 00:12:58,930
♪ See through the tricks,
truth and lies entwine ♪

291
00:12:59,130 --> 00:13:01,920
♪ Betting on black or white,
